            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. The Ads Manager tool itself is free — you only pay for the ads you run. There are no subscription fees, setup costs, or minimum spend requirements to access the platform.</p></div></div>
          </div>
